name: Timeland
description:
A farming game with a dark mood where you have to farm and sell your products in order to gain coins and win the game.

There's a day/night cycle.

We've made some 3D assets by ourselves and others taken from the Unity's asset store.

Musics taken from web.

This is our second GameJam: we've never made a farming game and we took this opportunity to make one our own way.

Thanks for playing :3
